translation.Name: Buak_Note_05
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Word around Buak is that there’s been some sightings of animal corpses ripped up in a really odd way, at first we only noticed it happenin’ to some poor deer, we thought it would’ve been a bear’s work. But then, we ran into some wolves and bears ripped up in the exact same manner. Whatever's out there in the forest is surely not too keen on our understanding of the food chain.
